      <div class="container">

              <div class="section" id="home" style="font-family: cursive; ">

              I am doing my Master's in Computer at University of Colorado Boulder. I am a passionate student and engineer who likes to work in recent technologies. <br><br>
              Before joining my Masters, I worked for 4+ years in Software Engineering. After my Bachelors, I joined IBM India as Associate System Engineer and worked on many projects to develop application for customers like AT&T <br><br>
              Then, I joined Cisco Systems as Automation Engineer where I worked on numerous tasks and learned a lot of things. My tasks were framework development, maintain/develop web scheduler, all kinds of testing (manual, automation, performance, longevity) and a few feature developments.<br><br>

              Please look at resume section for more details!!!<br><br>

              My hobbies are playing badminton, soccer and hiking.
          </div>
          <div class="section"  id="portfolio" style="font-family: cursive;">
              <div style="text-align: justify;">
                  <a href="https://github.com/samr13/Vulnerable-application-detection"><img src="images/img1.png" alt="Machine Learning vulnerable application classificatioin"  /></a>
                  <a href="https://medialistener.apollobit.com"><img src="images/img2.jpg" alt="Apollobit summer intern project"  /></a>
                  <a href="https://github.com/samr13/BigDataMonsters"><img src="images/img3.png" alt="NBA result prediction"  /></a>
                  <br><br>
                  More projects to be added. Design to be changed!!
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section" id="contact" style="font-family: cursive; ">
              <div class="chip green lighten-3 z-depth-4">
                    <a href="https://www.github.com/samr13">Github</a>
              </div><br><br>
              <div class="chip green lighten-3 z-depth-4">
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shyamrsundar">Linkedin</a>
              </div><br><br>
              <div class="chip green lighten-3 z-depth-4">
                  Email: shyam.ramamoorthy@colorado.edu
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section" id="resume" style="font-family: cursive; ">
              <div class="row">
                  <div class="col s12">
                      <ul class="tabs">
                          <li class="tab col s3"><a href="#educSection">Education</a></li>
                          <li class="tab col s3"><a href="#workSection">Work Experience</a></li>
                          <li class="tab col s3"><a href="#skillSection">Skills</a></li>
                      </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div align="center" id="educSection" class="col s12"><br>
                      <div style="margin-left: 25px; font-family: cursive" ng-repeat="e in education">
                          <h4 align="left">University: {{e.Univ}} </h4>
                          <p align="left">Course: {{e.Course}} </p>
                          <p align="left">GPA: {{e.GPA}} </p>
                          <p align="left">Coursework: {{e.Coursework}} </p>
                          <br>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div align="center" id="workSection" class="col s12" ><br>
                      <div style="margin-left: 25px; font-family: cursive" ng-repeat="w in work">
                          <h4 align="left">Organization: {{w.Company}} </h4>
                          <p align="left" >{{w.Position}} &nbsp;&nbsp; {{w.Period}} </p>
                          <p align="left"> {{w.Description}}</p>
                          </ul>
                          <br>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div align="center" id="skillSection" class="col s12"><br>
                      <ul ng-repeat="s in skills">
                          <font color="#ef5350">{{s.$id}}</font> : <font style="font-family: cursive">{{s.$value}}</font>
                      </ul>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>

      <script>
          $('.section').hide();
          $("#home").show();
          $(".link").click(function()
          {
              $('.section').fadeOut();
              $('#'+$(this).attr('name')).fadeIn();
          });


      </script>
    </body>
  </html>

